column4: RT @Georgetown On Tuesday March 5, @GtownDPS will conduct a full-scale response exercise with the @DCPoliceDept and @dcfireems. The exercise will take place at @YatesFieldHouse from 8 a.m. to 12 p.m. Yates will be closed during the exercise, and Hoyas are advised to avoid the area at that time.
